<c.bg_transparent>Your Kemocite shipment was tampered with.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:06:39.565 --> 00:06:40.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gralik.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:06:42.276 --> 00:06:43.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>He wasn't too happy when I told him</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:06:43.820 --> 00:06:45.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>what you were planning to do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with his Kemocite.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:06:45.780 --> 00:06:48.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be executed for this.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:06:49.951 --> 00:06:51.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:06:55.706 --> 00:06:58.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In the end,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it didn't make much of a difference.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:06:59.585 --> 00:07:02.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We didn't stop your program.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We only slowed it down.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:07:05.424 --> 00:07:08.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A few weeks later,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the weapon was launched.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:07:09.470 --> 00:07:11.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It destroyed my planet.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:07:15.184 --> 00:07:17.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were successful?</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:07:18.688 --> 00:07:20.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know if you'd call it a success.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:07:23.943 --> 00:07:29.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After Earth was destroyed,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the old Xindi rivalries surfaced again.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:07:30.158 --> 00:07:33.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Insectoids started attacking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>other Xindi colonies.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:07:33.494 --> 00:07:35.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They killed thousands of your people.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:07:37.290 --> 00:07:40.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Reptilians and Aquatics</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would never allow that.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:07:41.043 --> 00:07:43.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There wasn't a lot they could do.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:07:44.422 --> 00:07:47.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>While you were busy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>constructing the weapon,</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:07:47.341 --> 00:07:51.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Insectoids were secretly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>building hundreds of new ships.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:07:52.472 --> 00:07:54.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They used Earth as a diversion.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:07:54.974 --> 00:07:58.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Their real goal was to dominate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the other Xindi species.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:00.938 --> 00:08:02.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:04.150 --> 00:08:05.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's just a bloodworm.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:05.902 --> 00:08:07.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It'll work its way out.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:10.156 --> 00:08:11.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can you remove it?</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:35.806 --> 00:08:37.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hold still.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:09:33.781 --> 00:09:35.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you need this more than I do.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:09:39.328 --> 00:09:40.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Suit yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:43.499 --> 00:09:47.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand how a Xindi and a human</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:47.878 --> 00:09:50.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>could put aside</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their differences so quickly.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:50.631 --> 00:09:53.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles ) Trust me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it didn't happen overnight.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:55.261 --> 00:09:58.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You gave me this the first day</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we were locked up together.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:09:58.097 --> 00:09:59.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The guards thought</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it would be entertaining</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:09:59.557 --> 00:10:01.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to put us in the same cell.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:02.018 --> 00:10:04.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They even placed wagers on</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who would survive the longest.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:10:04.395 --> 00:10:08.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was in pretty bad shape at the time,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so you were the odds-on favorite.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:10:12.403 --> 00:10:14.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your people killed everyone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I ever cared about.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:10:17.575 --> 00:10:20.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was gonna make sure you never</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>walked out of that cell.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:10:21.454 --> 00:10:23.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For weeks, we tried to kill each other.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:10:25.499 --> 00:10:30.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was lying in the infirmary</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when I finally asked myself,</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:10:30.421 --> 00:10:33.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>what was the point?</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:10:35.593 --> 00:10:39.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My world was gone, but so was yours.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:10:42.141 --> 00:10:44.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So I made a proposal.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:10:46.103 --> 00:10:49.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The two of us would work together</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get out of that place.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:10:50.483 --> 00:10:52.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It took us longer than</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>either one of us thought.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:10:52.777 --> 00:10:54.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:10:54.445 --> 00:10:55.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here we are.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:10:59.241 --> 00:11:01.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't recognize this type of ship.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:11:02.536 --> 00:11:04.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a Malosian cargo shuttle.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:11:04.705 --> 00:11:06.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Malosian?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-They're traders.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:11:06.957 --> 00:11:11.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They bring supplies to the prison</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a few times a month.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:11:13.255 --> 00:11:17.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No weapons, but she's sturdy enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get us where we're going.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:11:19.720 --> 00:11:22.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps we should set a course</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:11:22.181 --> 00:11:24.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is it still in the expanse?</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:11:26.394 --> 00:11:27.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:11:31.774 --> 00:11:34.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When we were getting close</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to finding your weapon,</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:11:34.944 --> 00:11:37.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Insectoids sent their ships after us.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:11:38.531 --> 00:11:40.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They boarded </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and took me prisoner.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:11:42.952 --> 00:11:46.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then they planted spatial charges</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around our warp reactor.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:11:47.998 --> 00:11:50.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My crew was still aboard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when they detonated them.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:11:56.507 --> 00:11:59.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Insectoids were always</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>an aggressive species,</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:11:59.844 --> 00:12:01.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I never thought them capable of this.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:12:03.055 --> 00:12:05.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They destroyed everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Council worked for.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:12:05.850 --> 00:12:07.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Council?</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:12:07.351 --> 00:12:09.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was formed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when our planet was destroyed.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:12:09.103 --> 00:12:13.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was created to find a new homeworld</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for all Xindi.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:12:13.399 --> 00:12:16.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After years of searching,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we found a few suitable locations,</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:12:17.069 --> 00:12:20.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, as usual,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>couldn't agree on a final choice.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:12:20.698 --> 00:12:26.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our plan for reunification was put aside</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when we learned of the threat from Earth.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:12:27.788 --> 00:12:31.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was ordered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to begin designing the weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:12:32.376 --> 00:12:34.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I devoted years to it.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:12:34.378 --> 00:12:36.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I made so many sacrifices.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:12:36.589 --> 00:12:38.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So did my wife.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:12:40.176 --> 00:12:42.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do I know...</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:12:44.638 --> 00:12:46.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened to my family?</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:12:46.682 --> 00:12:51.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You told me you'd heard from Naara</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before you were sent to prison.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:12:52.813 --> 00:12:54.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She and the children were safe.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:13:02.406 --> 00:13:03.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have a ship now.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:13:05.284 --> 00:13:06.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can look for them.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:13:08.329 --> 00:13:10.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They were on a colony near a Red Giant.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:13:11.624 --> 00:13:14.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( computer beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:13:14.919 --> 00:13:17.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's nothing in range.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Do you remember the coordinates?</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:13:17.421 --> 00:13:18.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I doubt if there's anything left.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:13:18.631 --> 00:13:20.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It would've been one of the first colonies</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to have been attacked.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:13:21.008 --> 00:13:22.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There may have been survivors.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:13:23.844 --> 00:13:25.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's too dangerous.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:13:25.221 --> 00:13:28.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The patrol ships are still looking for us.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:13:29.433 --> 00:13:30.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should find a refuge in case--</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:13:30.893 --> 00:13:32.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( hissing )</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:13:34.104 --> 00:13:35.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reactor coolant.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:13:35.648 --> 00:13:37.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The conduit must have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ruptured in the attack.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:13:37.358 --> 00:13:39.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:13:52.373 --> 00:13:53.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Take it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What about you?</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:13:54.083 --> 00:13:55.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're the one with a family.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:13:56.835 --> 00:13:58.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You want to see them again?</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:14:01.882 --> 00:14:04.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Try to seal the rupture.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:14:04.468 --> 00:14:08.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll see if I can... ( coughs )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>close off the coolant tanks.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:14:09.056 --> 00:14:10.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:14:44.133 --> 00:14:45.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:14:45.134 --> 00:14:46.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:15:44.193 --> 00:15:45.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( hisses )</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:15:55.871 --> 00:15:57.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>T'Pol.</i></c.bg_transparent>

213
00:16:06.590 --> 00:16:09.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He should remain unconscious</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for at least two hours.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:16:09.718 --> 00:16:11.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The son of a bitch designed the weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:16:13.889 --> 00:16:15.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep an eye on him.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:16:15.891 --> 00:16:17.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trip.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:16:24.400 --> 00:16:27.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What have we got?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-There are seven Red Giants in this region</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:16:27.611 --> 00:16:30.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but they're spread over</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>approximately 40 light-years.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:16:30.322 --> 00:16:32.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can we scan them for a weapons facility?</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:16:32.282 --> 00:16:34.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs ) Not at this distance.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:16:34.326 --> 00:16:36.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This Red Giant might be a red herring.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:16:36.912 --> 00:16:39.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He only told you his family was</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>living near one of these stars.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:16:39.790 --> 00:16:41.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't know that the weapon's there.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:16:41.500 --> 00:16:42.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Degra's a senior official.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:16:43.043 --> 00:16:44.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We know he's designing the weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:16:44.712 --> 00:16:47.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a chance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he'd keep his family close by.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:16:47.297 --> 00:16:49.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For a moment I thought he was</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>gonna give you the coordinates.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:16:49.383 --> 00:16:51.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Too bad he didn't go for the Andorian ale.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:16:51.552 --> 00:16:53.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That would've loosened him up.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:16:53.429 --> 00:16:55.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You appear to have gained his trust.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:16:55.764 --> 00:16:58.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps you should try</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a more direct approach.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:16:58.684 --> 00:17:00.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean?</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:17:00.144 --> 00:17:02.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ask him where the weapon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is being constructed.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:17:02.813 --> 00:17:04.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's too risky.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:17:04.648 --> 00:17:08.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If he suspects something,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'll end up right back where we started.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:17:10.320 --> 00:17:11.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll tell me.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:17:14.950 --> 00:17:16.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just need a little more time.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:17:20.622 --> 00:17:24.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain's starlog,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>December 12, 2153.</i></c.bg_transparent>

239
00:17:24.376 --> 00:17:26.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We've returned to the site</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>where the Xindi</i></c.bg_transparent>

240
00:17:26.086 --> 00:17:28.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>were testing the prototype weapon.</i></c.bg_transparent>

241
00:17:28.505 --> 00:17:31.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>An analysis of the debris</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>may tell us more about it.</i></c.bg_transparent>

242
00:17:31.133 --> 00:17:32.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sensors beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:17:32.801 --> 00:17:35.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm picking up a ship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the edge of the system.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:17:37.848 --> 00:17:38.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's Xindi.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:17:40.809 --> 00:17:42.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Why didn't we see it before?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It may have been traveling</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:17:42.936 --> 00:17:45.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>through one of the subspace</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>vortices they use.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:17:45.647 --> 00:17:49.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Its hull signature matches the Xindi ships</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that were here two days ago.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:17:49.526 --> 00:17:52.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm reading three bio-signs on board.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:17:52.404 --> 00:17:54.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have they seen us yet?</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:17:54.782 --> 00:17:55.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't believe so.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:18:02.206 --> 00:18:03.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Set course for the inner moon.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:18:03.749 --> 00:18:06.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand by to deploy the sensor drones.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:18:06.627 --> 00:18:07.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:18:07.961 --> 00:18:09.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( alarm beeping )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:18:09.546 --> 00:18:11.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Weapons fire.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:18:11.090 --> 00:18:12.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>From where?</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:18:12.758 --> 00:18:15.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a ship closing.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's the human vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:18:15.260 --> 00:18:17.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You said there was no one in the system!</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:18:17.805 --> 00:18:19.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They must have been hiding in the debris.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:18:22.309 --> 00:18:24.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Contact the Council!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:18:24.895 --> 00:18:27.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They've disabled our subspace transceiver!</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:18:27.231 --> 00:18:28.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're making a run for it.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:18:28.941 --> 00:18:30.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>See what you can do about their engines.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:18:37.950 --> 00:18:39.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're not going anywhere, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:18:40.828 --> 00:18:41.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hail them.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:18:43.705 --> 00:18:45.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand down and prepare to be boarded.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:18:46.416 --> 00:18:47.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thalen.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:19:00.889 --> 00:19:02.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anything?</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:19:03.016 --> 00:19:04.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They were attempting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to erase the computer core</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:19:05.018 --> 00:19:06.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>when we boarded the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:19:06.770 --> 00:19:08.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's very little data left.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:19:08.147 --> 00:19:10.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about navigational logs?</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:19:12.151 --> 00:19:13.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They've been deleted.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:19:13.569 --> 00:19:15.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I may have something here, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:19:16.905 --> 00:19:19.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think these are fragments</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from a personal file.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:19:19.825 --> 00:19:24.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are parts of a letter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from someone named "Degra."</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:19:25.289 --> 00:19:27.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Does it mention the weapon?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No.</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:19:29.001 --> 00:19:32.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a reference to a planet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he visited recently.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:19:32.588 --> 00:19:34.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Azati Prime.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:19:34.423 --> 00:19:36.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me know what else you find.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:19:38.552 --> 00:19:41.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd love to spend an afternoon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>taking this engine apart.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:19:41.597 --> 00:19:43.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not your typical Nacelle configuration?</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:19:43.724 --> 00:19:47.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh-uh. Look how everything's tied in</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through their main deflector.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:19:47.477 --> 00:19:49.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Learn everything you can.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:19:50.063 --> 00:19:52.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( engines humming )</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:20:09.833 --> 00:20:11.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to know where</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're building the weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:20:12.211 --> 00:20:13.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what you're talking about.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:20:13.962 --> 00:20:15.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The hell you don't.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:20:17.799 --> 00:20:19.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your name is Degra.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:20:19.551 --> 00:20:21.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was at the Xindi colony</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:20:21.136 --> 00:20:23.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>when you picked up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your shipment of Kemocite.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:20:27.100 --> 00:20:30.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your people are planning another attack.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:20:30.938 --> 00:20:33.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not gonna let that happen.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:20:35.067 --> 00:20:38.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>By capturing us,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you've accomplished nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:20:39.863 --> 00:20:41.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where's the weapon?</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:20:45.369 --> 00:20:46.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Archer to the bridge, report.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:20:46.828 --> 00:20:48.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a surge in the plasma network.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:20:48.872 --> 00:20:50.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>What's causing it?</i></c.bg_transparent>

299
00:20:50.624 --> 00:20:54.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Radiation from the debris field.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's starting to affect our systems.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:20:54.461 --> 00:20:57.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, I recommend putting a safe distance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between us and the test site.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:20:57.756 --> 00:20:58.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> All right.</i></c.bg_transparent>

302
00:20:59.007 --> 00:21:01.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Take the ship out of the field</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>but keep us close by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

303
00:21:01.551 --> 00:21:02.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Understood.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:21:10.143 --> 00:21:14.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you won't tell me what I need to know,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>perhaps one of your men will.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:21:16.858 --> 00:21:21.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When my superiors learn we're missing,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they'll find your ship and destroy it.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:21:23.991 --> 00:21:25.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We could try a truth serum,</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:21:25.534 --> 00:21:30.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but it could take weeks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to synthesize the correct formula.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:21:30.163 --> 00:21:33.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been studying Xindi neurophysiology.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:21:33.792 --> 00:21:37.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It may be possible to erase</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>his most recent memory engrams.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:21:37.504 --> 00:21:40.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That way,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Degra will never know that he came aboard</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:21:40.173 --> 00:21:42.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or that he met any of us.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:21:42.301 --> 00:21:44.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But this is a Xindi-Reptilian.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:21:44.928 --> 00:21:46.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Would it work on a primate?</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:21:48.056 --> 00:21:50.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Their neural pathways</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are virtually identical.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:21:50.892 --> 00:21:52.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll need to perform a few tests,</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:21:52.519 --> 00:21:54.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, uh, I don't expect</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it will be a problem.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:21:54.771 --> 00:21:58.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How selective could this memory wipe be?</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:21:58.191 --> 00:22:00.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've built flight simulators</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for Starfleet training.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:22:00.193 --> 00:22:02.029 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This wouldn't be that different.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:22:02.112 --> 00:22:04.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not simply a matter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of constructing a shuttle.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:22:04.323 --> 00:22:05.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It has to be designed.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:22:05.907 --> 00:22:07.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What species built it?</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:22:07.409 --> 00:22:09.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What language will</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the control interface use?</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:22:09.286 --> 00:22:10.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hoshi can help with that.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:22:11.038 --> 00:22:14.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've recovered a letter Degra wrote</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to his wife a few months ago.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:22:14.124 --> 00:22:16.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Her name's Naara. They have two children.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:22:16.960 --> 00:22:18.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It may be necessary</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to communicate with you</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:22:18.920 --> 00:22:20.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>while you're inside the simulator.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:22:20.547 --> 00:22:23.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Macos use subdermal transceivers.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:22:23.717 --> 00:22:25.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're relatively easy to implant.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:22:27.054 --> 00:22:29.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's get started.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:22:29.181 --> 00:22:31.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol, I could use your help</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with some of the details.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:22:31.933 --> 00:22:33.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Details?</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:22:33.602 --> 00:22:35.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If he buys into this,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Degra's gonna want to know</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:22:35.228 --> 00:22:37.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>everything that's happened</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the last three years.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:22:37.564 --> 00:22:40.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't make up the whole story</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the spot.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:22:49.201 --> 00:22:50.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nice work.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:22:50.535 --> 00:22:51.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:22:51.995 --> 00:22:54.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dermal art used to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>very common on Denobula.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:22:54.581 --> 00:22:57.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fortunately,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my parents insisted I study it.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:22:57.834 --> 00:23:01.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've also stimulated his hair follicles.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:23:02.714 --> 00:23:05.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not sure about the gray.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:23:05.425 --> 00:23:07.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is only supposed to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>three years from now.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:23:07.803 --> 00:23:09.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, but you're forgetting about</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:23:09.346 --> 00:23:12.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the stress of imprisonment,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hmm, and torture!</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:23:12.224 --> 00:23:15.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It could very well have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>an effect on hair pigmentation.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:23:21.900 --> 00:23:25.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You're sure these are safe?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, yes.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:23:25.904 --> 00:23:30.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've treated patients with</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Regulan bloodworms for years.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:23:31.034 --> 00:23:32.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There should be no side effects</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:23:32.494 --> 00:23:36.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>aside from a thoroughly cleansed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>lymphatic system.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:23:36.373 --> 00:23:39.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please try not to injure it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They're difficult to replace.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:23:39.459 --> 00:23:41.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll do my best.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:23:50.220 --> 00:23:52.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rumbling, alarm beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:23:54.516 --> 00:23:55.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it?</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:23:55.976 --> 00:23:57.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Spatial anomalies.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:23:57.435 --> 00:23:59.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're passing through a field of them.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:24:01.148 --> 00:24:02.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hold on!</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:24:05.485 --> 00:24:06.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol to cargo bay 2.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:24:07.070 --> 00:24:09.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Increase hydraulics to level 6.</i></c.bg_transparent>

360
00:24:13.326 --> 00:24:16.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Is the hull lined with trellium?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Obviously not.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:24:18.456 --> 00:24:19.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Increase to level 7.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:24:20.959 --> 00:24:24.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>On my mark,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>initiate a sharp jolt to starboard.</i></c.bg_transparent>

363
00:24:24.254 --> 00:24:26.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How sharp do you want it?</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:24:27.048 --> 00:24:28.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sharp.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:24:29.885 --> 00:24:31.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You heard the lady.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:24:31.469 --> 00:24:32.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'POL: Let the Captain know.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:24:34.264 --> 00:24:36.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is gonna be a rough one, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:24:36.850 --> 00:24:40.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( rumbling continues )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:24:44.274 --> 00:24:46.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're losing structural integrity!</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:24:46.902 --> 00:24:48.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm taking us out of warp.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:24:54.326 --> 00:24:55.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( breathing heavily )</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:24:57.537 --> 00:24:59.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll never make it through</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this field in one piece.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:25:03.335 --> 00:25:05.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can we go around?</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:25:07.339 --> 00:25:08.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't have enough fuel.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:25:12.469 --> 00:25:14.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should send a distress call.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:25:15.972 --> 00:25:18.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>One of your ships might be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>close enough to hear it.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:25:18.808 --> 00:25:20.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if the Insectoids pick it up?</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:25:22.395 --> 00:25:24.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't have a lot of choices.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:25:27.400 --> 00:25:29.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a com channel used by</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>high-ranking primate officials.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:25:29.861 --> 00:25:32.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I doubt the Insectoids know it.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:25:33.531 --> 00:25:35.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's the frequency?</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:25:35.450 --> 00:25:37.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It would be easier for me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to enter it directly.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:25:49.339 --> 00:25:50.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ensign?</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:25:55.428 --> 00:25:57.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I've got it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Stand by to respond.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:25:57.764 --> 00:26:00.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( communicator beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-MALCOLM: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Bridge to command center.</i></c.bg_transparent>

386
00:26:00.350 --> 00:26:03.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm picking up a distortion in subspace.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:26:03.228 --> 00:26:04.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe it's a Xindi ship.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:26:04.771 --> 00:26:07.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How long until they arrive?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-About six hours.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:26:07.440 --> 00:26:10.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Their sensors are pretty sophisticated.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They might see us long before then.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:26:12.237 --> 00:26:15.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>take us back into the debris field.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:26:15.699 --> 00:26:18.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALCOLM: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>The radiation could overload</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>our systems again.</i></c.bg_transparent>

392
00:26:18.159 --> 00:26:19.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm aware of the risks.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:26:21.288 --> 00:26:22.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Carry out my orders.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:26:22.664 --> 00:26:24.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Acknowledged.</i></c.bg_transparent>

395
00:26:28.169 --> 00:26:30.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( exhales )</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:26:30.380 --> 00:26:34.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>One of the inmates told me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all about Maarek III.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:26:35.802 --> 00:26:39.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He used it as a staging area</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when he was smuggling dilithium.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:26:39.264 --> 00:26:41.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did he say it was like?</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:26:41.099 --> 00:26:42.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:26:42.809 --> 00:26:44.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Beautiful.</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:26:45.145 --> 00:26:48.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>With beaches that go on</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for thousands of kilometers.</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:26:51.109 --> 00:26:55.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>First thing I'm gonna do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is find a cold lake</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:26:55.447 --> 00:26:58.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and take the longest bath of my life.</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:27:01.244 --> 00:27:04.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>It sounded a lot like Earth,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>the way he described it.</i></c.bg_transparent>

405
00:27:09.711 --> 00:27:11.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Captain's certainly drinking a lot.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:27:11.921 --> 00:27:15.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The doctor gave him an anti-intoxicant.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:27:15.216 --> 00:27:19.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>This colony of yours,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>you never told me about it.</i></c.bg_transparent>

408
00:27:19.137 --> 00:27:20.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>It was bleak, desolate.</i></c.bg_transparent>

409
00:27:20.805 --> 00:27:22.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The planet was barely habitable.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:27:22.891 --> 00:27:24.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why'd you live there?</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:27:24.851 --> 00:27:27.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't by choice.</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:27:28.104 --> 00:27:29.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Naara was desperate to leave.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:27:29.689 --> 00:27:31.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She didn't think a military habitat</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:27:31.441 --> 00:27:34.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>was the right environment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the children.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:27:34.569 --> 00:27:38.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you have a family, Captain?</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:27:42.035 --> 00:27:44.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's been a long time since</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>anyone called me "Captain."</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:27:45.038 --> 00:27:48.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's Jonathan, remember?</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:27:48.208 --> 00:27:51.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never really had an opportunity</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to start one.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:27:53.254 --> 00:27:54.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was away from home a lot.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:27:56.508 --> 00:27:58.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should make the time.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:27:59.719 --> 00:28:03.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've learned that our work,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the end, means very little.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:28:04.474 --> 00:28:06.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our real legacy is the children.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:28:10.271 --> 00:28:13.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would do anything to protect mine.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:28:15.819 --> 00:28:21.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After I was told of the threat</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from humanity...</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:28:22.450 --> 00:28:26.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I left my theoretical studies</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and agreed to design the prototype weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:28:27.205 --> 00:28:29.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When it arrived in your star system,</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:28:30.792 --> 00:28:34.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I watched the incoming telemetry</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the other members of the Council.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:28:35.922 --> 00:28:38.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seven million lives...</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:28:40.051 --> 00:28:42.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Were extinguished in front of my eyes.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:28:43.513 --> 00:28:49.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I asked myself,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how many of those were children?</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:28:53.857 --> 00:28:55.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose I've told you this before.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:28:59.529 --> 00:29:00.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, you haven't.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:29:01.740 --> 00:29:03.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Three years!</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:29:03.324 --> 00:29:06.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My children may not even</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>recognize me after so much.</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:29:06.619 --> 00:29:08.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:29:16.337 --> 00:29:18.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're being hailed.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:29:18.173 --> 00:29:20.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( static )</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:29:20.425 --> 00:29:24.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Whoever it is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they must be pretty far away.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:29:24.179 --> 00:29:26.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll try to clear it up.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:29:26.389 --> 00:29:28.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>HOSHI (AS THALEN):</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i></i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Are you receiving this transmission?</i></c.bg_transparent>

441
00:29:28.850 --> 00:29:31.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>This is Thalen,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>responding to your distress call.</i></c.bg_transparent>

442
00:29:31.478 --> 00:29:32.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Please acknowledge.</i></c.bg_transparent>

443
00:29:32.729 --> 00:29:35.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's one of my colleagues.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:29:35.231 --> 00:29:38.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thalen! Can you hear me? It's Degra!</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:29:38.735 --> 00:29:41.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Degra? It's good to hear your voice.</i></c.bg_transparent>

446
00:29:41.488 --> 00:29:42.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'd... I'd heard from my sources</i></c.bg_transparent>

447
00:29:42.989 --> 00:29:45.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that you'd been captured</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by the Insectoids.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:29:46.075 --> 00:29:48.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There were reports</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you had been executed.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:29:48.745 --> 00:29:51.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DEGRA: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>They haven't killed me yet.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>I need your help.</i></c.bg_transparent>

450
00:29:51.372 --> 00:29:53.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My friend and I have escaped</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from an Insectoid prison.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:29:54.000 --> 00:29:56.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Their patrols are looking for us.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:29:56.252 --> 00:29:59.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>HOSHI:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Uh, I'm losing your signal.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Please repeat.</i></c.bg_transparent>

453
00:29:59.631 --> 00:30:00.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: Better make it fast!</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:30:02.091 --> 00:30:05.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thalen, where are you?</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:30:05.094 --> 00:30:08.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm on Azati Prime.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>It... It... It's safe here.</i></c.bg_transparent>

456
00:30:08.431 --> 00:30:10.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is my family still there? Are they safe?</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:30:10.934 --> 00:30:12.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( static )</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:30:12.143 --> 00:30:13.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thalen!</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:30:13.603 --> 00:30:16.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Naara is here and the children.</i></c.bg_transparent>

460
00:30:16.731 --> 00:30:18.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'll... I'll tell them to expect you.</i></c.bg_transparent>

461
00:30:19.067 --> 00:30:20.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( static )</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:30:22.070 --> 00:30:23.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( line disconnects )</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:30:25.573 --> 00:30:27.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At least you know they're all right.</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:30:27.158 --> 00:30:31.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There were more than 1,000 primates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and Arboreals at that colony.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:30:31.371 --> 00:30:33.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why it wasn't destroyed.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:30:33.623 --> 00:30:38.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We should still change course.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Do you know the coordinates?</i></c.bg_transparent>

467
00:30:42.549 --> 00:30:44.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:30:44.175 --> 00:30:45.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must forgive me.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:30:46.845 --> 00:30:49.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To me, it's been only a day</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since we were enemies.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:30:50.014 --> 00:30:52.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Giving you the coordinates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to a classified installation</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:30:52.559 --> 00:30:55.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is... difficult.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:30:56.104 --> 00:30:57.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be my guest.</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:31:03.027 --> 00:31:04.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're coming in.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:31:04.237 --> 00:31:08.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>1127.4 by 4052...</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:31:08.533 --> 00:31:11.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>by 3901.1.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:31:11.953 --> 00:31:13.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:31:14.247 --> 00:31:15.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A Red Giant.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:31:15.874 --> 00:31:17.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open a com line to the Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:31:22.213 --> 00:31:25.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You encrypted the navigation controls.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:31:25.425 --> 00:31:26.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:31:26.676 --> 00:31:31.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'POL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain, the coordinates match</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>the location of one of the Red Giants.</i></c.bg_transparent>

482
00:31:31.264 --> 00:31:34.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you mind if I ask how long</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it will take to get there?</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:31:34.267 --> 00:31:36.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs ) Not long.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:31:36.561 --> 00:31:38.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'POL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Approximately three weeks</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>at maximum warp.</i></c.bg_transparent>

485
00:31:38.938 --> 00:31:41.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A considerable detour</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if the weapon isn't there.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:31:52.410 --> 00:31:54.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What will your people think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when you show up with me?</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:31:56.706 --> 00:31:59.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Humans probably aren't</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their favorite species.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:31:59.918 --> 00:32:02.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll tell them everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you did to help me.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:32:02.503 --> 00:32:05.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a senior official.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>There won't be any problems.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:32:08.384 --> 00:32:09.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I appreciate that.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:32:09.636 --> 00:32:11.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a diverse community.</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:32:11.721 --> 00:32:14.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Far more pleasant than most military--</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:32:14.182 --> 00:32:16.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:32:18.728 --> 00:32:22.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Travis?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-The port hydraulics are acting up.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:32:28.404 --> 00:32:29.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shut them down.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:32:32.784 --> 00:32:34.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're not responding.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:32:34.285 --> 00:32:36.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( over communicator )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>T'Pol to cargo bay 2. Report.</i></c.bg_transparent>

498
00:32:36.621 --> 00:32:40.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The radiation from the debris</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is overloading the hydraulic system.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:32:40.458 --> 00:32:42.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can you stabilize the simulator?</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:32:42.085 --> 00:32:43.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>TUCKER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>I'm working on it.</i></c.bg_transparent>

501
00:32:43.169 --> 00:32:45.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-More anomalies?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm not sure.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:32:46.297 --> 00:32:48.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain, we're having some problems.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Stand by.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:32:50.969 --> 00:32:53.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol to the bridge.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Take us out of the debris field.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:32:54.013 --> 00:32:55.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALCOLM: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Understood.</i></c.bg_transparent>

505
00:33:11.781 --> 00:33:14.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( beep )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-MALCOLM: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Bridge to the command center.</i></c.bg_transparent>

506
00:33:14.117 --> 00:33:16.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We're clear of the debris field.</i></c.bg_transparent>

507
00:33:16.369 --> 00:33:17.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Acknowledged.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:33:17.620 --> 00:33:19.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What was the problem?</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:33:19.789 --> 00:33:21.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Subspace turbulence.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:33:22.208 --> 00:33:23.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really?</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:33:29.298 --> 00:33:32.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm curious... Jonathan.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:33:35.471 --> 00:33:38.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we've been friends</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for as long as you say,</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:33:38.975 --> 00:33:41.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I must have told you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the names of my children.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:33:41.853 --> 00:33:44.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You still don't believe me, do you?</i></c.bg_transparent>

515
00:33:44.147 --> 00:33:45.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's something in his hand.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:33:45.815 --> 00:33:47.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Magnify.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:33:47.608 --> 00:33:49.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>It's been years</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>since you've said anything.</i></c.bg_transparent>

518
00:33:50.028 --> 00:33:51.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain, he has a weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:33:51.738 --> 00:33:55.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just need you to tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what their names are.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:33:55.616 --> 00:33:56.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're coming in.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:33:56.993 --> 00:33:59.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>This isn't necessary.</i></c.bg_transparent>

522
00:33:59.746 --> 00:34:00.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Piral and Jaina.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:34:02.707 --> 00:34:04.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Piral and Jaina.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:34:06.544 --> 00:34:07.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Which one is older?</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:34:12.091 --> 00:34:13.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not in here, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:34:13.301 --> 00:34:14.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( scoffs )</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:34:16.763 --> 00:34:18.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:34:21.184 --> 00:34:22.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:34:35.656 --> 00:34:38.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll never find the weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:34:38.159 --> 00:34:39.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take him to the brig.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:34:45.666 --> 00:34:47.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( panting )</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:34:56.052 --> 00:34:57.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens )</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:35:00.556 --> 00:35:03.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were told humans were ruthless.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:35:03.476 --> 00:35:07.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I didn't know you were</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>also skilled at deception.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:35:07.647 --> 00:35:09.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When did you realize?</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:35:09.398 --> 00:35:12.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had my suspicions from the beginning,</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:35:12.610 --> 00:35:16.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but it was the com signal</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from my colleague on Azati Prime</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:35:16.739 --> 00:35:18.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that confirmed them.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:35:18.157 --> 00:35:20.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We know your ship has been there...</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:35:20.827 --> 00:35:21.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Recently.</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:35:22.537 --> 00:35:26.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's an insectoid deuterium</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>facility on Azati Prime.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:35:27.041 --> 00:35:29.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's the last place</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my people would have gone</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:35:29.460 --> 00:35:30.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to hide from them.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:35:30.920 --> 00:35:35.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it weren't for that one mistake,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your plan might have succeeded.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:35:35.383 --> 00:35:37.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You gave us the coordinates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of a Red Giant.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:35:38.970 --> 00:35:41.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I gave you...</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:35:41.931 --> 00:35:45.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>what you thought you wanted.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:35:49.605 --> 00:35:52.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess I'll just have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to wipe your memory clean again.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:35:52.525 --> 00:35:55.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go back into the simulator</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and start this whole thing over.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:35:56.154 --> 00:35:58.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I doubt there's time for that.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:35:58.239 --> 00:36:00.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We both know my people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are searching for me.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:36:00.700 --> 00:36:03.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you didn't figure it out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until after the malfunction.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:36:05.121 --> 00:36:08.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd be willing to bet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>those coordinates are real.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:36:09.208 --> 00:36:14.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I suggest you proceed there</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at maximum warp!</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:36:14.213 --> 00:36:17.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why would he encrypt the coordinates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if they weren't accurate?</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:36:17.175 --> 00:36:19.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps he thought it would make</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>them appear more convincing.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:36:19.844 --> 00:36:21.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's got to be lyin', sir.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:36:21.888 --> 00:36:23.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Something must have happened</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>during the radiation surge</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:36:23.764 --> 00:36:25.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that tipped him off.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:36:26.601 --> 00:36:29.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can't afford to lose three weeks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if the weapon isn't there.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:36:32.565 --> 00:36:36.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you learned anything more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about how they open the subspace vortices?</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:36:36.319 --> 00:36:39.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They use some kind of</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>phase deflector pulses.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:36:39.322 --> 00:36:42.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Once they're in, their ships can travel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>half a dozen light-years</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:36:42.825 --> 00:36:44.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in a couple of minutes.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:36:46.704 --> 00:36:49.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to see all the data</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you've collected.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:37:00.843 --> 00:37:02.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( beep )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Archer to the bridge.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:37:02.511 --> 00:37:03.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We're ready.</i></c.bg_transparent>

568
00:37:04.722 --> 00:37:06.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tactical alert.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:37:08.684 --> 00:37:09.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Engage.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:37:14.023 --> 00:37:15.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:37:33.042 --> 00:37:34.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open it.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:37:34.252 --> 00:37:35.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:37:39.215 --> 00:37:41.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You two, come with me.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:37:41.133 --> 00:37:42.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I said move!</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:37:46.806 --> 00:37:49.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll fracture the hull</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if this goes on any longer.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:37:53.646 --> 00:37:55.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>FEMALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Hull breaches</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>on decks "D" and "E."</i></c.bg_transparent>

577
00:37:55.731 --> 00:37:57.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Emergency bulkheads!</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:37:57.358 --> 00:37:59.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You're the engineer?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:37:59.235 --> 00:38:00.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're gonna help us.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:38:00.403 --> 00:38:02.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We adapted your technology,</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:38:02.321 --> 00:38:04.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>used our main deflector</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to open a subspace vortex.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:38:04.365 --> 00:38:05.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's impossible.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:38:07.451 --> 00:38:11.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The vortex is starting to collapse.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I need you to stabilize it.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:38:11.747 --> 00:38:14.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't do what he says,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this ship will break apart.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:38:19.505 --> 00:38:20.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant!</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:38:22.341 --> 00:38:24.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell him to do what he's told.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:38:24.385 --> 00:38:26.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do nothing to help them!</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:38:28.889 --> 00:38:30.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The pylons are buckling!</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:38:33.227 --> 00:38:36.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>HOSHI: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Engineering,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>we're losing hull integrity.</i></c.bg_transparent>

590
00:38:36.272 --> 00:38:39.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( alarm beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:38:49.452 --> 00:38:51.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( panting )</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:38:51.245 --> 00:38:53.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trip!</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:38:53.122 --> 00:38:54.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't me, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:38:55.458 --> 00:38:57.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll be damned.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:38:58.544 --> 00:39:00.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Travis inverted the warp field.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:39:01.339 --> 00:39:03.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It dropped us back into normal space.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:39:03.549 --> 00:39:05.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( over communicator )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>T'Pol to Captain Archer.</i></c.bg_transparent>

598
00:39:05.718 --> 00:39:06.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:39:06.969 --> 00:39:08.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Please report to the bridge.</i></c.bg_transparent>

600
00:39:12.141 --> 00:39:14.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take him back to the brig.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:39:24.403 --> 00:39:25.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Report.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:39:25.571 --> 00:39:28.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've reached the coordinates.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Ensign, magnify.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:39:33.245 --> 00:39:35.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm picking up several Xindi vessels.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:39:35.831 --> 00:39:38.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm also reading significant quantities</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of Kemocite.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:39:38.417 --> 00:39:40.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's our status?</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:39:40.669 --> 00:39:42.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Minimal damage.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:39:42.380 --> 00:39:44.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The hull plating is coming back online.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:39:44.840 --> 00:39:46.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Arm all weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:39:47.009 --> 00:39:49.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lay in a course</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for those Kemocite signatures.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:39:49.845 --> 00:39:51.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Full impulse.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:39:54.392 --> 00:39:56.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get him out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:39:56.560 --> 00:39:58.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll never get close to the weapon!</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:39:58.729 --> 00:40:01.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our defense perimeter will destroy you!</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:40:16.789 --> 00:40:17.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Show him.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:40:27.800 --> 00:40:29.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks for your help.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:40:29.593 --> 00:40:31.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take him to sick bay.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:40:47.278 --> 00:40:48.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:40:49.864 --> 00:40:52.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you overdid the turbulence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>just a little, Ensign.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:40:53.701 --> 00:40:55.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll try to do better next time, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:41:08.007 --> 00:41:09.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How's it coming?</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:41:09.925 --> 00:41:12.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've made it appear as if</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a plasma conduit ruptured,</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:41:13.762 --> 00:41:15.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>rendering them unconscious.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:41:15.598 --> 00:41:18.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm injecting them with</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>trace amounts of the plasma.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:41:18.517 --> 00:41:20.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't be harmful.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:41:21.687 --> 00:41:25.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This accident won't explain how</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their computer core was deleted.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:41:25.274 --> 00:41:29.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As long as they don't know we were here,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can leave them with a mystery.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:41:29.570 --> 00:41:31.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( communicator beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:41:31.739 --> 00:41:34.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALCOLM: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>The Xindi vessel</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>is less than an hour away, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

629
00:41:37.578 --> 00:41:40.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain's starlog, supplemental.</i></c.bg_transparent>

630
00:41:40.164 --> 00:41:42.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Hopefully the journey to Azati Prime</i></c.bg_transparent>

631
00:41:42.333 --> 00:41:45.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>will be the final leg in our search</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>for the Xindi weapon.</i></c.bg_transparent>

